title: Ilyse Lipman's goal in OT sees Byram Hills past Bronxville
text: Facebook Email Twitter Google+ LinkedIn Pinterest Ilyse Lipman's goal in OT sees Byram Hills past Bronxville In a rainy game, Jessica Kennett scored two first-half goals and Ilyse Lipman scored in overtime in a 3-2 win.
